<div class="row about-container">
   <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-6 about-text-container">
      <div id="about-heading"><h2>Who are we?</h2><hr></div>
      <p>“In the long run the practice of solidarity proves much more advantageous to the species than the development of individuals endowed with predatory inclinations.” - Pyotr Kropotkin</p>
      <p>Our team of designers and engineers wanted to benefit modern man, instead of engaging in "predatory inclinations." GoodNeighbor was designed with Kropotkin's words in mind; that we live and survive better as a species with compassion and community. Here, we can exchange our services amongst our community with the help of modern technology in a recognizable framework.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-6 about-image-container">
      <img id="about-image-company" src="../img/about-us.jpg">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row offer-container">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-6 offer-image-container">
      <img src="../img/working.jpg">
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-6 offer-text-container">
      <div id="offer-heading"><h2>What do we offer?</h2><hr></div>
      <p>“Practicing mutual aid is the surest means for giving each other and to all the greatest safety, the best guarantee of existence and progress, bodily, intellectual and moral.”</p>
      <p>GoodNeighbor offers a digital space for our borader communities to interact, engage with, and provide for each other. Do you need your brakes changed? Your door fixed? Help building a fence? Generate a request and either wait for other members of the community to respond in your inbox, or search other requests in our city/town and message those community members to suggest an exchange.</p>
      {{#if logged_in}}
      <a href="/dashboard">Go to dashboard</a>
      {{else}}
      <a href="/signup">Sign up today</a>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>
